%!PS

%	This example appears in section "More About Bezier Curves"
%	in Chapter 7 - "Arcs and Curves".
%

/inch { 72 mul } def			%  define inch procedure
8.25 inch 5.5 inch moveto		%  set current point
8.25 inch 7.708 inch			%  first Bezier control point
6.458 inch 9.5 inch			%  second Bezier control point
4.25 inch 9.5 inch			%  end point of Bezier curve
curveto					%  draw Bezier curve
0.125 inch setlinewidth			%  fat line width
stroke					%  paint path
showpage				%  display page
